    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_7111369457798908941.png",
                "id": "talent38222",
                "key": "迅烈傾霜拳",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "迅烈傾霜拳"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素傷害</span>，本角色附屬<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">寒烈的懲裁</span>。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">寒烈的懲裁</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">角色進行普通攻擊時：</span>如果角色生命至少為6，則此技能少花費1個<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素</span>，傷害+1，且對自身造成1點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透傷害</span>。</p><p>如果角色生命不多於5，則使此傷害+1，並且技能結算後治療角色2點。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/d16aaeb6e3d7c751f1ac36d875668e80_2380596404848612313.png",
                "id": "talent66727",
                "key": "冰牙突馳",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰牙突馳"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素傷害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">餘威冰錐</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">本角色在本回合中受到傷害或治療每累計到2次時：</span>此技能少花費1個元素骰（最多少花費2個）。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">餘威冰錐</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方選擇行動前：</span><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 228, 217)\">造成2點</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素傷害</span><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 228, 217)\">。</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1</span><br></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/866bcc4723d1e09e478894bf4d1e70ef_5121350995662658093.png",
                "id": "talent81053",
                "key": "黑金狼噬",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "黑金狼噬"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超導</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">凍結</span>：本傷害+1，使目標本回合無法行動（受到<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>傷害后提前解除，但是傷害+2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_6856061133997412890.png",
                "id": "talent68229",
                "key": "冰元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>穿透傷害無法受到傷害加成，但是也無法被護盾、傷害免疫等效果抵消。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_1956185845948618673.png",
